These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: satire, animation, superhero, epic, sports, action, martial-arts
7 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, rat, bird, horse, hamster, fish, goldfish
 1. the person watching satire movies is between the person watching epic movies and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
 2. the person watching animation movies is in the middle##1
 3. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 4. the person watching sports movies is between the owner of the bird and the owner of the hamster##2
 5. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
 6. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
 7. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the owner of the horse and the owner of the bird##2
 8. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 9. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
10. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
11. the person watching action movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | satire | martial-arts | animation    | superhero | sports   | action    |
| Pet         | fish  | rat   | horse | guinea-pig | bird   | goldfish | hamster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, swisher, bluemaster, dunhill, game, old-henry, montecristo
There are 7 different favourite colors: pink, black, ebony, blue, turquise, green, emerald
1. the person who likes green is on the far left##1
2. the bluemaster-smoker is between the old-henry-smoker and the person who likes green##2
3. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
4. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
5. the swisher-smoker is in the middle##1
6. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
7. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
8. the game-smoker is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
9. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person who likes pink##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Cigar          | game | bluemaster | old-henry | swisher | montecristo | tiparillo      | dunhill  |
| Color   | green | blue  | emerald     | ebony     | turquise  | pink | black |

