.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: singing, board-games, cooking, puzzles, magic-tricks, photography, woodworking
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: rock, disco, house, electronic, country, ambient, gospel
 1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 2. the fan house is on the left of the fan electronic##1
 3. the fan country is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 5. the fan rock is on the left of the fan gospel##1
 6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the fan electronic##1
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the fan house##1
 8. the fan rock is between the fan gospel and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
 9. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the fan ambient##1
10. the person who's hobby is board-games is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Hobby   | woodworking | magic-tricks | singing | board-games   | puzzles | cooking | photography |
| Music-Genre           | country | ambient     | disco     | house | electronic   | rock   | gospel    |

