.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
7 different games are played: mah-jongg, backgammon, canasta, domino, poker, scrabble, whist
There are 7 different favourite colors: turquise, black, emerald, ebony, white, aquamarine, apricot
 1. the person playing whist is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
 2. the person playing poker is on the right of the person who likes white##1
 3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
 4. the person playing poker is on the right of the person who likes white##1
 5. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 6. the person who likes ebony is between the person playing canasta and the person who likes aquamarine##2
 7. the person playing mah-jongg is in the middle##1
 8. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person playing domino##1
 9. the person playing backgammon is the person who likes black##1
10. the person who likes turquise is the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Game      | canasta    | poker  | domino  | mah-jongg  | whist      | scrabble       | backgammon |
| Color   | white | ebony | aquamarine | apricot | turquise | emerald | black  |

