1. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
2. the montecristo-smoker is the person who growsdaisy##1
3. the chaman-smoker is between the person who growsazalea and the person who growstulip##2
4. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
5. the chaman-smoker is in the middle##1
6. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
7. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
8. the bongani-smoker is the person who growssunflower##1
9. the person who growszinnia is the cain-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Flower   | sunflower      | zinnia | tulip | poppy | azalea      | daisy      | orchid |
| Cigar     | bongani | cain | fonseca       | chaman | siglo | montecristo | vegafina |

