 6. the victorian house is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 7. the person playing domino is the victorian house##1
 8. the townhouse house is the person playing canasta##1
 9. the person playing billiard is between the person playing canasta and the ranch-style house##2
10. the farmhouse house is on the left of the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| House   | victorian | craftsman    | futuristic | farmhouse   | townhouse | modern    | ranch-style |
| Game      | domino | backgammon | chess    | whist | canasta    | billiard | bridge  |

